tags: [[Special Rule]]
title: Skyfire
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A model with this special rule, or that is firing a weapon with this special rule, fires using its normal Ballistic Skill when shooting at [[Flyer]]s, [[Flying Monstrous Creature]]s and [[Skimmer]]s, but it can only fire Snap Shots against other targets.